  "remarks": "TAi.100 Title: Maulavi. Designation: Acting, Governor of Kunduz Province under the Taliban regime.  Alternative title:  Sar Muallim.  Reconciled after the fall of the Taliban regime, and assumed duties under the new Government on district level in Kunduz Province. Confirmed assassinated by Taliban on 9 November 2008.; Listing: Listed by UN 1267 Committee on 23 February 2001 (amended on 21 Sep 2007, 18 May 2012 and 31 Dec. 2013)",
